                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Winthrop</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Brussels</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-09-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 20, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Winthrop reports the death on Friday, September 19, at 7.25 o’clock p.m., of
                    Her Majesty the Queen of Belgium.)</p>
            </div>
